12 Sec. 1. RESIDENTIAL UNIVERSAL DESIGN STANDARDS; STUDY
13 COMMITTEE; REPORT
14 (a) Creation. There is created the Residential Universal Design Study
15 Committee to explore implementation of statewide universal design standards
16 for all residential buildings.
