17 (c) Powers and duties. The Committee shall study the development and
18 implementation of statewide universal design standards for residential
19 buildings, including identification and analysis of the following issues:
20 (1) existing federal and state laws regarding Americans with Disabilities
21 Act, 42 U.S.C. §§ 12101–12213, standards and building codes;
